Simple Spring boot application to send: 
1. Simple email with text body. 
2. Email with attachment

Important :- 
Before Running this application make sure to do below steps. As they are required for configuration.

A)
Go to Gmail -> Manage Your Google Account -> Security -> App Password -> Choose other(Custom.
name from the drop down) and click on "Generate" -> 
Note down the generated password and use it in application.properties

B)
Check the main class and give the file name according to your PC/